WEBVTT

00:00:04.420 --> 00:00:08.310
THIS IS TAPE FOR OF THE INTERVIEW BEING CONDUCTED IN MELBOURNE, AUSTRALIA

00:00:08.310 --> 00:00:11.650
WITH LEIBUSH LICHTENSTEIN ON THE FIRST OF MARCH

00:00:11.650 --> 00:00:13.180
NINETEEN NINETY EIGHT

00:00:14.350 --> 00:00:17.980
in di letste tashme hot men geredt vegn

00:00:17.980 --> 00:00:20.880
vegn Yisroel un dayn lebn dortn, un

00:00:20.902 --> 00:00:23.682
u di sibes far vos bist gekumen keyn MELBOURNE.

00:00:23.450 --> 00:00:24.238
yo.

00:00:24.936 --> 00:00:28.524
di sibe iz gevezn far vos ikh bin gekumen keyn MELBOURNE

00:00:28.986 --> 00:00:30.296
far derfar

00:00:31.281 --> 00:00:35.629
vayl der zun hot nisht gehat dortn vos tsu tun, nisht z- nisht lernen zikh

00:00:36.276 --> 00:00:37.957
un nisht gehat keyn arbet

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:42.727
un Moyshe iz geven nokhn militer.

00:00:42.727 --> 00:00:44.066
me ken nisht lozn

00:00:44.595 --> 00:00:47.576
aza yat ken men nisht lozn stam azoy.

00:00:48.274 --> 00:00:51.291
bist ongekumen in MELBOURNE, vu bistu geshtanen?

00:00:52.932 --> 00:00:54.833
bin arayn tsu di tokhter.

00:00:56.138 --> 00:00:59.406
s'ersht iz geforn der, Moyshe iz geforn, der zun iz geforn.

00:01:00.508 --> 00:01:04.130
un hot ongehoybn a bisele arbetn

00:01:06.685 --> 00:01:09.340
hot ge- getseykhnt fentster

00:01:09.340 --> 00:01:10.543
in BUILDINGS.

00:01:11.629 --> 00:01:12.838
dos iz geven di arbet.

00:01:12.996 --> 00:01:14.593
fardint demolt, ⟨kh'veys⟩

00:01:15.308 --> 00:01:18.038
dray doler tsi dray un fuftsik a sho

00:01:18.050 --> 00:01:19.910
un vos hostu getun ⟨tsun ersht⟩?

00:01:19.008 --> 00:01:20.881
ikh bin nisht geforn demolt. ikh

00:01:20.826 --> 00:01:21.394
ah

00:01:20.881 --> 00:01:22.761
ikh, s'ersht iz er geforn.

00:01:23.256 --> 00:01:25.258
nu, iz er geven bay di shvester

00:01:26.125 --> 00:01:27.621
⟨un⟩ shpeter

00:01:28.842 --> 00:01:30.405
bin ikh geforn

00:01:31.457 --> 00:01:33.999
UNK gebn a kuk vos hert zikh do azoy.

00:01:34.663 --> 00:01:36.260
kh'bin do ahergekumen

00:01:36.773 --> 00:01:38.336
bin ikh shoyn nisht tsurikgeforn

00:01:38.612 --> 00:01:39.770
⟨fun⟩ Yisroel

00:01:41.751 --> 00:01:43.629
bin ahergekumen als imigrant

00:01:43.629 --> 00:01:44.783
un der eydem hot

00:01:45.075 --> 00:01:46.621
hot gut gezogt far mir

00:01:47.286 --> 00:01:48.607
az ikh darf nisht

00:01:48.607 --> 00:01:51.110
farlangen fun, fun GOVERNMENT gornisht

00:01:51.977 --> 00:01:54.570
un ikh hob mir gedungen a FLAT

00:01:55.757 --> 00:01:57.472
far tsvey toyznt doler

00:01:58.187 --> 00:02:00.133
dakht zikh mir a halb yor

00:02:00.133 --> 00:02:03.221
fertsik doler a vokh. demolt geven a sakh gelt.

00:02:03.694 --> 00:02:05.944
dos iz gevezn azoy in

00:02:06.102 --> 00:02:07.851
zibetsikstn yor.

00:02:08.127 --> 00:02:09.302
geven a sakh gelt.

00:02:09.443 --> 00:02:11.361
hob gevoynt a halb yor in a FLAT

00:02:12.733 --> 00:02:14.566
un keyn arbet hob ikh nisht gehat.

00:02:16.294 --> 00:02:18.347
bin geganen arbetn oyf a plats

00:02:18.572 --> 00:02:22.363
hob ikh gearbet epes a khoydesh tsayt. ⟨s'iz gekumen⟩ far a yontev

00:02:22.437 --> 00:02:23.766
far rosheshone

00:02:23.766 --> 00:02:24.897
bikhdey

00:02:24.897 --> 00:02:27.340
zol men nisht darfn batsoln far yontev UNK

00:02:29.254 --> 00:02:31.340
hot er mir gemakht tsores, ikh zol avekgeyn.

00:02:31.617 --> 00:02:34.496
bin ikh avekgeganen. hot zikh gedreyt a halb yor tsayt.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.195
hot men gefunen

00:02:36.195 --> 00:02:37.955
a anons in di tsaytung

00:02:38.265 --> 00:02:39.896
az me zukht a CUTTER.

00:02:41.573 --> 00:02:43.035
veyst vos heyst a CUTTER?

00:02:43.210 --> 00:02:44.233
shnayder

00:02:44.526 --> 00:02:46.967
in a KNITTING fabrik, FACTORY.

00:02:48.745 --> 00:02:51.152
bin ikh geganen in di KNITTING FACTORY

00:02:51.529 --> 00:02:53.733
un ikh hob dortn ongehoybn tsu arbetn.

00:02:55.275 --> 00:02:57.221
kh'hob ongehoybn tsu arbetn

00:02:57.221 --> 00:02:58.897
bay a gevisn Goldberg

00:02:59.764 --> 00:03:03.133
hot er mir gezogt "vest do" zogt er "arbetn bay mir.

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:04.837
do vestu gut fardinen.

00:03:05.333 --> 00:03:06.862
vestu gut fardinen."

00:03:07.392 --> 00:03:10.339
s'iz geven demolt der prayz, ikh gedenk nisht,

00:03:10.412 --> 00:03:12.279
gedenk nisht vifl der prayz

00:03:12.420 --> 00:03:14.692
"vest" zogt er "arbetn fir sho OVERTIME

00:03:16.993 --> 00:03:19.248
vest arbetn shabes biz tsveleve

00:03:19.862 --> 00:03:21.813
vestu tsuzamennemen a bisl gelt."

00:03:22.697 --> 00:03:26.623
bin arayn dortn arbetn. ikh hob UNK, bin gevorn

00:03:27.591 --> 00:03:29.407
a CUTTER by KNITTING

00:03:30.814 --> 00:03:33.693
un di froy hot ongehoybn tsu arbetn in di heym

00:03:34.408 --> 00:03:36.882
UNK aheymgebrengt a shnayd mashin

00:03:37.665 --> 00:03:39.667
un ikh hob ir tsugeshnitn

00:03:39.842 --> 00:03:40.865
a bisl

00:03:41.260 --> 00:03:44.393
kinder SKIRTkelekh, veyst vos heyst SKIRTkelekh?

00:03:44.702 --> 00:03:48.543
kinder heyzelekh fun, fun JEANS, farshidene skhoyres

00:03:49.528 --> 00:03:51.243
un gegebn tsu makhn

00:03:51.975 --> 00:03:53.977
di mentshelekh, vi heyst dos?

00:03:55.249 --> 00:03:57.926
un m'iz dos geforn shabes un zuntik

00:03:58.135 --> 00:03:59.361
oyf a MARKET

00:04:00.058 --> 00:04:01.554
un m'hot dos farkoyft.

00:04:01.577 --> 00:04:04.389
s'ershte hob ikh dos arayngenumen in di FACTORY

00:04:05.931 --> 00:04:07.933
tsu di PRESSERS ⟨iz gan⟩ arbetn

00:04:08.901 --> 00:04:11.865
hot zi gearbet dortn in di PRESS in di FACTORY

00:04:13.845 --> 00:04:16.674
aza, azoy lang biz s'iz gevezn

00:04:16.765 --> 00:04:18.159
biz detsember

00:04:19.060 --> 00:04:21.939
un dortn hot, dort hot men sheyn fardint, hot fardint

00:04:22.131 --> 00:04:23.407
bay hundert un tsv-

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:25.314
un tsvontsik doler hot zi fardint

00:04:25.742 --> 00:04:28.233
durkh tsvontsik sho arbet.

00:04:28.594 --> 00:04:30.258
geven demolt a sakh gelt.

00:04:31.817 --> 00:04:34.764
nu, iz zi geganen oyf an OPERATION in HOSPITAL

00:04:35.563 --> 00:04:38.307
oyf di, oyf di fis, di beyner ⟨tseshnaydn⟩

00:04:38.550 --> 00:04:39.961
iz zi tsurikgekumen

00:04:40.542 --> 00:04:41.919
fun di FACTORY

00:04:41.959 --> 00:04:43.995
hot men ir gevolt gebn azan arbet

00:04:44.558 --> 00:04:46.611
zol fardinen bloyz oyf di ⟨shpayzn⟩.

00:04:47.140 --> 00:04:49.473
hob ikh gezogt "veys" zog ikh "vos?" mayn vayb.

00:04:49.473 --> 00:04:50.778
"for shnel aheym."

00:04:51.814 --> 00:04:53.613
⟨gegan⟩ hob ikh gebrengt a mashin

00:04:53.772 --> 00:04:55.149
a shnayd mashin

00:04:56.539 --> 00:04:58.777
un m'hot gekoyft a bisele skhoyre

00:04:59.256 --> 00:05:00.887
un zi iz gezesn

00:05:01.163 --> 00:05:02.490
a gantse vokh

00:05:03.205 --> 00:05:05.393
un zi hot dos oyfgearbet

00:05:05.803 --> 00:05:07.901
⟨un bin⟩ geforn oyfn MARKET farkoyfn.

00:05:07.901 --> 00:05:08.986
un far dem hot

00:05:09.043 --> 00:05:11.264
hot men tsuzamengeshtelt a bisl gelt

00:05:11.389 --> 00:05:13.560
un m'hot UNK m'hot gekoyft dos.

00:05:14.443 --> 00:05:17.643
farshteyt zikh, m'hot getsolt, ikh hob getsolt TAX fun di arbet

00:05:17.987 --> 00:05:20.731
un zi hot shpeter batsolt TAX fun zikh.

00:05:21.008 --> 00:05:23.415
un dayn vayb vo- lebt nokh?

00:05:23.775 --> 00:05:27.329
⟨vu⟩ lebt zi? shoyn, ⟨zekstn⟩ yor lebt zi shoyn nisht.

00:05:29.682 --> 00:05:31.408
un di tokhter vi iz yetst?

00:05:31.408 --> 00:05:32.729
di tokhter in MELBOURNE.

00:05:33.192 --> 00:05:33.861
un der zun?

00:05:34.896 --> 00:05:36.662
der, vemes zun?

00:05:36.178 --> 00:05:37.083
dayn zun.

00:05:36.887 --> 00:05:39.007
mayn zun hostu haynt gezen.

00:05:39.925 --> 00:05:41.505
er iz gut ayngeordnt.

00:05:42.895 --> 00:05:44.948
un vegn

00:05:46.337 --> 00:05:48.595
di yidishe zakhn, du, du, ge-

00:05:48.595 --> 00:05:51.647
du geherst tsu a, a, a shul do?

00:05:51.855 --> 00:05:52.794
yo.

00:05:53.121 --> 00:05:54.770
ikh gey in shul arayn.

00:05:54.150 --> 00:05:55.940
velkhe shul geyst?

00:05:55.041 --> 00:05:56.371
ale tog

00:05:56.371 --> 00:05:58.509
for ikh in di shul arayn, davn in di fri

00:05:58.509 --> 00:05:59.611
KATANGA.

00:05:59.905 --> 00:06:01.671
veyst vu di KATANGA iz?

00:06:01.035 --> 00:06:01.765
yo.

00:06:02.638 --> 00:06:06.867
un tsurik brengt mikh a khaver frieirt, tsurik aheymgefirt, un ikh hob a transport.

00:06:07.026 --> 00:06:09.332
nor zuntik, aza tog vi haynt

00:06:09.422 --> 00:06:12.943
kumt er nokh bay di fri un nemt mikh tsum davenen, brengt mir tsurik.

00:06:13.185 --> 00:06:15.153
ikh hob nisht keyn transport, kumt er nokh.

00:06:15.717 --> 00:06:18.242
azoy iz ga- azoy firt zikh dos lebn

00:06:18.636 --> 00:06:20.216
un ikh hob genumen

00:06:20.610 --> 00:06:23.641
kh'hob mikh ayngeordnt mit a froy. host gezen dos.

00:06:24.407 --> 00:06:26.004
un ikh voyn mit ir.

00:06:27.006 --> 00:06:28.383
zi kokht far mir.

00:06:29.014 --> 00:06:30.257
ikh es bar ir.

00:06:30.432 --> 00:06:31.556
batsol ir

00:06:32.203 --> 00:06:33.716
un dos iz dos lebn.

00:06:38.228 --> 00:06:40.635
far vos iz di milkhome forgekumen?

00:06:40.641 --> 00:06:41.478
vu?

00:06:41.940 --> 00:06:43.031
in Eyrope.

00:06:43.594 --> 00:06:45.360
far vos iz es forgekumen?

00:06:46.125 --> 00:06:47.199
in EUROPE?

00:06:49.416 --> 00:06:51.317
di milkhome iz forgekumen

00:06:51.778 --> 00:06:53.645
 dos heyst in

00:06:54.141 --> 00:06:56.126
in nayn un draysikstn yor

00:06:55.457 --> 00:06:56.193
yo

00:06:56.841 --> 00:06:58.792
vayl di DEUTSCHEN

00:06:59.423 --> 00:07:01.509
hobn farlangt fun Poyln

00:07:01.819 --> 00:07:03.315
a shtik erd.

00:07:04.165 --> 00:07:06.218
vayl di ershte velt milkhome

00:07:06.747 --> 00:07:09.491
hot Poyln tsugenumen bay DEUTSCHLAND

00:07:11.083 --> 00:07:12.460
DEUTSCHE erd

00:07:14.037 --> 00:07:15.560
un dos iz geven

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:17.321
di zakh iz gevezn

00:07:17.530 --> 00:07:19.650
far vos in DEUTSCHLAND

00:07:20.095 --> 00:07:22.958
iz geven a groyse arbetslozikeyt

00:07:26.338 --> 00:07:28.323
biz Hitler iz gekumen tsu di makht.

00:07:28.633 --> 00:07:30.331
Hitler iz gekumen tsu di makht

00:07:30.523 --> 00:07:32.592
in dray un draysikstn yor

00:07:32.768 --> 00:07:34.365
hot er zey tsugezogt

00:07:35.333 --> 00:07:38.415
az er vet zey makhn, zoln kenen lebn.

00:07:38.978 --> 00:07:40.896
dos iz, dos iz geven di sibe.

00:07:41.256 --> 00:07:44.524
zey hobn dokh ongehoybn mit Poyln. dos ersht iz gevezn

00:07:44.563 --> 00:07:45.536
Poyln.

00:07:46.217 --> 00:07:48.033
der koridor iz geven bay Tshekhn.

00:07:48.158 --> 00:07:49.142
Tshekhn

00:07:49.142 --> 00:07:50.008
Poyln.

00:07:50.048 --> 00:07:53.130
zey hobn gevolt s- tsurik dos shtik erd bay Poyln.

00:07:53.338 --> 00:07:55.158
un Poyln hot gezogt loy.

00:07:55.158 --> 00:07:56.336
gezogt az nisht.

00:07:56.967 --> 00:07:59.880
Poyln hot tsugezogt Rusland

00:08:01.253 --> 00:08:04.453
hobn zey s'er- di ershte tsayt gezogt az zey veln zey gebn hilf

00:08:05.218 --> 00:08:06.742
hot der poylisher

00:08:06.742 --> 00:08:08.723
general, RYDZ SMIGLY

00:08:09.201 --> 00:08:12.232
hot er gezogt az er vil nisht hobn keyn poylishn shtivl

00:08:12.829 --> 00:08:13.515
oyf

00:08:13.555 --> 00:08:16.012
keyn rusishn shtivl oyf di poylishe erd.

00:08:16.947 --> 00:08:18.426
dos iz gevezn.

00:08:18.702 --> 00:08:20.923
nu, azoy iz damolt ongefaln

00:08:21.132 --> 00:08:22.993
DEUTSCHLAND iz ongefaln demolt

00:08:22.993 --> 00:08:24.787
Tshekhn, nokh Poyln

00:08:24.945 --> 00:08:28.196
un azoy tsugenumen di ale, di ale kleyne lendelekh.

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:31.386
dos iz geven di sibe, far m'hot gefodert.

00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:35.570
dos arbetslozikeyt iz gevezn dortn shtark groys

00:08:35.712 --> 00:08:37.495
hot men ongehoybn mit di yidn.

00:08:37.888 --> 00:08:41.763
di yidn hobn di ⟨farmegenise⟩ yidn zenen groyse doktoyrim

00:08:41.922 --> 00:08:45.234
groyse advokatn, groys gelernte

00:08:45.234 --> 00:08:47.095
yidn hobn di ⟨farmegenise⟩

00:08:47.322 --> 00:08:50.356
hot men zikh fartshepet tsu dem. m'hot ongehoybn tsu brenen dortn

00:08:50.356 --> 00:08:52.853
koydem di yidishe farmegns, di shuln.

00:08:52.853 --> 00:08:54.707
m'hot geharget, m'hot geshlogn

00:08:55.337 --> 00:08:57.136
un nokh zenen zey ongefaln

00:08:57.160 --> 00:09:00.444
oyf Poyln. dos iz geven di sibe.

00:08:59.030 --> 00:09:00.470
du host geleyent "mayn kamf"

00:09:00.470 --> 00:09:01.593
far di milkhome?

00:09:00.552 --> 00:09:02.250
neyn.

00:09:02.340 --> 00:09:04.224
ikh hob nisht gehat keyn tsayt tsu dem.

00:09:08.989 --> 00:09:10.333
vos far a

00:09:13.798 --> 00:09:16.306
gedanken hostu vegn, vegn

00:09:16.971 --> 00:09:21.825
di yidntum, yidntum in, in, in di milkhome vos iz forgekumen?

00:09:22.472 --> 00:09:25.267
vos ken ikh hobn saran, saran gedanken

00:09:26.944 --> 00:09:30.501
ikh bin demolt gevezn, ikh bin demolt geven in Rusland. vos hob ikh gekent

00:09:30.501 --> 00:09:32.476
vos hob ikh gekent trakhtn vegn dem?

00:09:32.476 --> 00:09:34.801
kh'hob getrakht a sakh, nor ikh hob gornisht gekent tun.

00:09:34.881 --> 00:09:36.161
vos hostu getrakht?

00:09:36.192 --> 00:09:37.901
kh'hob getrakht az s'iz shlekht.

00:09:37.901 --> 00:09:39.341
kh'hob gehert grusn

00:09:40.039 --> 00:09:41.687
vos di DEUTSCHEN tuen.

00:09:41.811 --> 00:09:44.218
m'hot gehert vos di DEUTSCHEN tuen mit di rusn.

00:09:45.507 --> 00:09:47.883
hobn zey di rusn oykhet umgebrengt

00:09:47.883 --> 00:09:49.078
milyonen.

00:09:50.974 --> 00:09:53.156
s'iz geven demolt zeyer a shvere kamf.

00:09:53.156 --> 00:09:55.069
un vos hot men zey gekent helfn?

00:09:55.581 --> 00:09:57.301
vos hob ikh gekent dortn tun?

00:09:57.301 --> 00:09:59.391
ikh hob dortn gehat amolt a tsaytung?

00:09:59.428 --> 00:10:01.852
m'hot gekrign a tsaytung, m'hot gedorfn hobn

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:04.083
in CHEMIST arayntsugeyn

00:10:04.083 --> 00:10:07.083
hot men gemuzt hobn mit a fleshele, zol hobn oyfn meditsin.

00:10:07.410 --> 00:10:08.956
s'iz dort gornisht geven.

00:10:08.980 --> 00:10:10.830
Rusland iz gornisht gevezn.

00:10:11.224 --> 00:10:14.629
ven di milkhome hot zikh geendikt un host zikh dervust vegn di f-

00:10:14.629 --> 00:10:16.803
di zakhn vos zenen forgekumen

00:10:18.565 --> 00:10:24.640
vos, vos hostu ts- fun dem aroysgenumen? vos far a gedanken hostu fun dem?

00:10:24.353 --> 00:10:27.705
vos hob ikh geke- vos hob ikh gekent UNK saran gedanken?

00:10:28.268 --> 00:10:30.557
di froy, azoy az m'iz gekumen keyn Poyln

00:10:30.917 --> 00:10:33.121
bin ikh geven in dos, in

00:10:33.499 --> 00:10:36.682
oyf di farnumene gebitn, DEUTSCHE gebitn vos Poyln

00:10:37.718 --> 00:10:40.074
Poyln hot tsugenumen bay zeyers, m'hot ⟨zi⟩ gegebn

00:10:41.582 --> 00:10:45.122
un dernokh bin ikh arayngeforn keyn tsentral Poyln. demolt hob ikh zikh dervust

00:10:45.122 --> 00:10:46.351
vos hot pasirt.

00:10:46.611 --> 00:10:48.157
hob getrofn dortn

00:10:48.383 --> 00:10:50.942
kuzinkes. kh'hob getrofn bakante

00:10:51.032 --> 00:10:53.467
hot mir ales dertseylt. zey zenen geven

00:10:53.467 --> 00:10:55.903
biz tsun lager zenen geven in di geto

00:10:56.533 --> 00:10:58.450
biz m'hot zey genumen in lager arayn

00:10:58.862 --> 00:11:02.568
hobn zey mir dertseylt vos hot pasirt. zey hot men genumen in lager arayn

00:11:02.980 --> 00:11:07.524
un vos hot pasirt mit mayn vayb's foter, mit mayn vayb's eltern

00:11:07.524 --> 00:11:09.065
di shvestern, bridern.

00:11:09.679 --> 00:11:13.723
dos hob ikh gevoyr gevorn. un di froy mayne iz arayngeforn keyn Pshedbuzh demolt

00:11:13.982 --> 00:11:16.153
dos iz geven in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

00:11:16.227 --> 00:11:17.723
keynem nisht getrofn.

